OL,5, Tory leadership contender Liz Truss has
OL,6, defended her plans to lower taxes,     
OL,7, describing them as the best way to     
OL,8, avoid a recession.                     
OL,10,FShe was speaking after she had told a  
OL,11,Fpaper she favoured lowering taxes over 
OL,12,F"giving out handouts" to help          
OL,13,Fhouseholds hit by higher fuel bills.   
OL,15,FOn a visit to Solihull, she said       
OL,16,Flowering taxes would help ease the cost
OL,17,Fof living crisis.                      
OL,19,FHer rival Rishi Sunak wants to tackle  
OL,20,Finflation before cutting taxes.        
